reviewText: Would not play on my DVD/BlueRay unit. I am very disappointed because I was really looking forward to watching this.

Seeing this video is the next best thing to visiting these incredible ancient (yet local) sites in person!  But this video/photo/reference montage provides a lot of background information on many of the sites, plus provides reasonable about their probable origins.

If you have any interest in unpublicized historical treasures you can explore that are right under our noses in America, this will intrigue you!
